item.title: How do i make my self an admin in my own sever
item.dc:creator: @Retard_Monkey Retard Monkey
item.description:
@Retard_Monkey wrote:

If I understand you right, your problem is you can’t make yourself admin?
Go into your character files, into the account you want to promote and change the “Player-Rights” to:
1 for Mod,
2 for Admin,
3 for Owner,
4 for hidden Admin
or 10 for hidden Owner.
